{"tid":2017950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喪鐘都敲爛，戰火味都聞到鼻塞，究竟香港人幾時先肯放棄冇用嘅抗爭工具？","createTime":"2020-05-15T10:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T02:21:31.000Z","uid":35699,"like":26,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd41ece43c50411288a7a5a5d295e971b5d543e2","tid":2017950,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:42:36.000Z","msg":"我冇話咩，你唔鍾意勇武咪放棄勇武，唔鍾意泛民咪放棄泛民囉<br />\n<br />\n喺度婆婆媽媽，呢個又要留，嗰個又同路人，留住啲垃圾喺身邊，抗爭自然寸步難行<br />\n<br />\n共產黨擅長將戰事拖長，待敵人（即係你呀懵撚）意志資源消耗殆盡，再一舉擊潰。抗爭時間越長，手足開始流亡或入獄，意志開始轉為啲舒服嘅方法，共產黨就開始好似依家咁郁手整死你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講定先，樓主五毛分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b05cef65e5d3234ae4cce387730d73edf32490d","tid":2017950,"uid":266503,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"要有放棄陳地的心理準備 要有斷箭的決心（要求友軍轟炸自己的陣地）要求美國取消香港政策法"},{"pid":"5d440bf9919d12938fd683067ff63591ebeeea31","tid":2017950,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b05cef65e5d3234ae4cce387730d73edf32490d","tid":2017950,"uid":266503,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"要有放棄陳地的心理準備 要有斷箭的決心（要求友軍轟炸自己的陣地）要求美國取消香港政策法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bf3ed28187bbebd0dd729bf3238176b95e1831","tid":2017950,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"分化！"},{"pid":"5a389596981e5897f46f57607402d69ada8e35fa","tid":2017950,"uid":304769,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劇本黎，支共明顯想玩鎖國，要拉埋香港落水咁解姐<br />\n<br />\n支共想攬炒，我地唯有奉陪，誠懇呼籲外資盡快撤出香港，以保安全<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，唯有開戰<br />\n<br />\n向愛爾蘭共和軍學習<br />\n<br />\n向愛爾蘭獨立學習<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，任何行動<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不受傷不被捕</strong></span>真係最重要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139aaf6b8beb909c478636ef83812cfc783ed347","tid":2017950,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"慘推"},{"pid":"e3ba9532c463c4833cc5f4b0e0b7008d07775ac3","tid":2017950,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"事實就係和理非已經無空間"},{"pid":"e04b43a804c4d1d770112a9263d8a9e59dca4baa","tid":2017950,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3ba9532c463c4833cc5f4b0e0b7008d07775ac3","tid":2017950,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"事實就係和理非已經無空間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"有啲路線真心要放棄，香港人唔可以再貪心話「唔同路線並行」，與其浪費人手喺啲冇用嘅路線製造假希望，倒不如咩都唔柒做"},{"pid":"95e9eb14cdbad3ca52d498d1acf611cf05096383","tid":2017950,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3ba9532c463c4833cc5f4b0e0b7008d07775ac3","tid":2017950,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"事實就係和理非已經無空間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"其實我同意和平理性非暴力，which is 好似iron man 咁用激光射到敵人化灰，咁咪夠晒和理非囉"},{"pid":"1bade83838b8492dfa3efef478da0661024eac50","tid":2017950,"uid":66221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:23:50.000Z","ms